                <origin>Richmond Whig, Baltimore American, Philadelphia Evening Journal</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Quotes from various newspapers regarding the positive progress in the
